## Problem 3: BDD closes without waiting

### Symptom
The After hook runs before the step actually finishes — test passes when it
should fail, or page is blank in failure screenshot.

### Root cause
Missing `await` somewhere in the promise chain, OR the step returns before
the navigation triggered by the action completes.

### Fix: wrap navigating clicks with explicit post-navigation wait

```ts
// OLD (closes before navigation completes):
When('I click Login', async function(this: PwCraftWorld) {
  await this.action.click(this.find.byRole('button', { name: 'Login' }));
  // Step returns here — but page is still navigating!
});

// NEW:
When('I click Login', async function(this: PwCraftWorld) {
  const smart = new SmartWaitHelper(this.page);
  await this.action.click(this.find.byRole('button', { name: 'Login' }));
  await smart.forPageReady({ timeout: 60_000 });
  // OR if you know where it should go:
  await this.wait.forUrl('/dashboard', 60_000);
});
```

