## Problem 4: Converting codegen's locator strategy

Codegen generates brittle locators. Here's how to translate them:

| Codegen output | pw-craft equivalent | Why better |
|---|---|---|
| `page.locator('#form-1234')` | `find.byTestId('checkout-form')` | IDs change, testids don't |
| `page.locator('button:nth-child(3)')` | `find.byRole('button', { name: 'Continue' })` | Position-independent |
| `page.locator('input[type="checkbox"]').nth(2)` | `find.checkboxByLabel('Same address')` | Semantic, reads like spec |
| `page.click('text=Submit')` | `find.byRole('button', { name: 'Submit' })` | Role-scoped, avoids false matches |
| `page.locator('.mat-checkbox-input')` | `find.checkboxByLabel('Remember me')` | Survives Angular Material upgrades |

