## Cucumber config timeout reference

```js
// cucumber.config.cjs
module.exports = {
  // ...your config...
};

// In hooks.ts — must be at module level, before hooks:
setDefaultTimeout(3 * 60 * 1000); // 3 minutes per step

// For a specific slow step only, use a tagged timeout:
Before({ timeout: 5 * 60 * 1000 }, async function(this: PwCraftWorld, scenario) {
  await this.init(scenario.pickle.name);
});
```

